(March 18, 1953.)

Max Eisenberg, on Behalf of Himself and All Other Stockholders of Central Zone Property Corporation, Similarly Situated, v. Central Zone Realty, Inc., et al.

— Motion for leave to appeal to the Court of Appeals granted. Settle order on notice. Present — Dore, J. P., Cohn, Callahan, Van Voorhis and Bergan, JJ. [See ante, pp. 817, 874.]
